data.description: Huntingtown School district. Welcome home to this fenced and corner lot  with brick front colonial and pool, shed, finished basement with 5th bedroom, full bath and family room that walks out to the patio area. You must see this one and make it your own. Owner's have loved and cared for the home and all is ready for you. In 2023, Vinyl Plank flooring in main level family room and kitchen with bamboo flooring in foyer and new washer for clothes. In 2022 new cover and filter for the in ground pool. In 2021, new carpet in bedrooms and basement was installed, New 16 SEER HVAC for lower 2 levels as well as in kitchen  new refrigerator and new stove top burners. In 2020, new roof, new siding on side of home, new garage door openers and shed added to rear yard. In 2019, a new dishwasher, painted garage floor, new waste pump in basement and new risers for septic tank. In 2018, carpet runner on stairs and sunsetter shade for deck area in rear. All is here that you will need or want as the warmer weather comes. Be that "house" that everyone wants to come and spend the day at!
